Secret Screen commands
Home:5, FF:3, RW:2.............Secret Screen
Home:5, U, R, D, L, U..........Secret Screen 2
Home:5, U, D, U, D, U..........Wi-Fi Secret Screen
Home:5, FF, PP, RW, PP, FF.....Platform Secret Screen
Home:5, FF, D, RW, D, FF.......Antenna Secret Screen
Home:5, RW:3, FF:2.............Bit Rate Override
Home:3, U:2, R, L, R, L, R.....Channel Info
Home:3, U:2, L, R, L, R, L.....Developer Settings
Home:5, R, L, R, L, R..........Network
Home:5, U, RW:2, FF:2..........Reboots Device



Enter into the secret screen.
* Go to the Home screen
* Home(5x) Fast Forward - Down - rewind - Down - Fast Forward
This takes you on the Roku 3 Platform Secret Screen
Options
  * Systems Operations Menu
  * Enable Travel Connect ( this indicates currently disabled)
  * Wi-Fi Remote Menu
  * WiFI Secret Screen
  * Cancel

  WiFI Secret Screen
Output shows:
  AP: What you are currently connected to
  Signal Strength:
  Antenna 1: Number
  Antenna 2: Number
  Glitch/sec: Number
  Channel:
  Joins
  TX: frames: retries: PER:
  RX: frames: retries: PER:
  Error:

  Menu Options:
  *Resets
  *Interference
  *Radios
  *Power
  *Cancel
